::DarkMouse::

She saw Terrorsaur looking at her growling.  She wasn't sure if he hated her 
just because she was female, a mouse, or both.  She knew that per Megatron's 
orders, she had to get a long with him, like it or not.
She went to a small energon dispenser.  Put two cubes on a tray and walked 
over to Terrorsaur.

"Here you are."  She didn't smile at all.  She really didn't like being that 
close to a bot who could swallow her whole in one gulp.  It made her 
nervous, but she did her best to hide it.
"If there is anything else that you require, let me know."
She turned and walked back to her console.
